    Interface Description
    IFileDescriptor
    Since jserv 1.4.11, a file is an object shared across nodes, so this interface is also used for synchronizing.
    IProfileResolver
    Resolving file's saving folder etc., e.g.
    parse "yyyy_MM" as folder from file's sharing date or creating date;
    or handle sharer on ending of chain push.
